"Inevitable" doesn't scare me.

652
00:25:21,634 --> 00:25:23,979
Let's go off bypass.

653
00:25:24,003 --> 00:25:25,614
I-I was careful. I...

654
00:25:25,638 --> 00:25:27,249
I don't know if you used
the wrong amount of pressure

