00:30:51,775 --> 00:30:53,853
How?

760
00:30:53,877 --> 00:30:56,022
Massive pulmonary artery embolism.

761
00:30:56,046 --> 00:30:57,290
The bone cement...

762
00:30:57,314 --> 00:30:58,525
Okay, wait, I don't want
to hear it from you.

